<HEADLINE> Union Furor Makes Twinkies Scarce  </HEADLINE>
By DAVID SHARP, Associated Press Writer
<TEXT>
<P>
   PORTLAND, Maine (AP) -- The Teamsters' stranglehold on shipments
of Interstate Bakeries Corp. products spread throughout the
Northeast Monday, creating some shortages of Wonder Bread, Twinkies
and other products.
</P>
<P>
   A Philadelphia bakery was shut down after pickets appeared
Monday, and Teamsters planned to set up pickets in Buffalo, N.Y.,
as well. A New York City bakery also was shut down over the
